Care. PVTs invoice part of the admission price to the insurance institutions as a ‘care allowance’.</li><li>The remainder of the admission price is paid by the care user themselves to the PVT. This personal contribution may be further reduced by a fixed allowance.</li></ul><p>The Department of Care calculates the admission price for the psychiatric care homes and communicates these prices to the PVTs and the insurance institutions.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.zorg-en-gezondheid.be/financiering-en-facturatie-voor-psychiatrische-verzorgingstehuizen\">Additional information on financing and invoicing</a></p>"},"naam":{"en":"Cost"},"@type":"Kost","order":0}],"creatie":"2010-07-22T13:34:36Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2023-11-14T15:46:50Z","laatstOntvangen":"2024-03-28T10:10:20.2567463Z","productnummer":"440","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"en":"See also on vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be"},"url":"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/Product/1ae1d092-0ac2-41d2-85aa-3ac8d2c31347"},"metadata":{"uJeVersie":"34.3.0","generatedFormeleFields":false,"generatedInformeleFields":true},"@id":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantiesnapshot/681a3f7f-d531-4c9e-98f0-59a814d38b34","@type":"InstantieSnapshot","isVersionOf":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantie/49d87cf4-8365-4e4d-9e17-fbea3e1e97dd"},{"id":"5ee4028a-7f15-4402-99ec-23838d1d6b6b","generatedAtTime":"2024-03-28T10:10:19.890472Z","bevoegdBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"uitvoerendBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Erkenning van algemene ziekenhuizen","nl-BE-x-formal":"Erkenning van algemene ziekenhuizen","nl":"Erkenning van algemene ziekenhuizen"},"beschrijving":{"nl":"<p>De Vlaamse overheid is bevoegd voor de programmatie, het toezicht en de erkenning van de algemene ziekenhuizen in Vlaanderen en Brussel. </p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>De Vlaamse overheid is bev